DocAttribute.Documentation:
Particular type of the assignment relationship. It can constrain the applicable object types, used within the role of _RelatedObjects_. { .change-ifc2x4}
> IFC4 CHANGE&nbsp; The attribute is deprecated and shall no longer be used. A NIL value should always be assigned.
> IFC4.3.0.1-CHANGE The attribute type has been changed to IfcStrippedOptional given that IfcObjectTypeEnum has been deleted.
